      "role": "Computer_terminal",
      "content": "exitcode: 0 (execution succeeded)\nCode output: ['0-4-0' '4-4-0' '2-6-0' '2-8-0' '2-6-4' '2-8-4' 'NW2' 'F3' 'PA' 'GP15'\n 'GP30' 'RDC' 'Brill' 'PCC' 'Handcar']\n"
